    "engine": "knitr",
    "markdown": "---\nlisting:\n  - id: index-blog\n    contents:\n      - \"blog/*/*.qmd\"\n      - \"blog/*/*.md\"\n    sort: \"date desc\"\n    type: grid\n    max-items: 9\n    page-size: 3\n    categories: false\n    sort-ui: false\n    filter-ui: false\n    fields: [title, image, description, date]\nformat:\n  hebstr-template-html:\n    grid:\n      sidebar-width: 0px\n      body-width: 1500px\n      margin-width: 0px\n---\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n::: {.index-logo .column-screen}\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"index-logo-libelle\">\n  <p><strong>A</strong>ssociation <strong>L</strong>illoise</p>\n  <p>des <span class=\"strong-i\">i</span>nternes</p>\n  <p>de <strong>S</strong>anté <strong>P</strong>ublique</p>\n</div>\n<div\n  class=\"index-logo-lille\"\n  role=\"img\"\n  aria-label=\"Symbole de Lille, fleur de lys rouge\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"index-logo-alisp-social\">\n  <div class=\"index-logo-alisp\"><p>AL<span class=\"strong-i\">i</span>SP</p></div>\n  <div class=\"index-logo-social\">\n      <a\n    href='{{< var social.mail.href >}}'\n    title='Email'\n    aria-label='Email'\n    >\n    <iconify-icon\n      icon='fa6-solid:envelope'\n      width='1.5em'\n      height='1.5em'\n      aria-hidden='true'>\n    </iconify-icon>\n  </a>\n      <a\n    href='{{< var social.insta.href >}}'\n    title='Instagram'\n    aria-label='Instagram'\n    target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <iconify-icon\n      icon='fa6-brands:instagram'\n      width='1.5em'\n      height='1.5em'\n      aria-hidden='true'>\n    </iconify-icon>\n  </a>\n      <a\n    href='{{< var social.twitter.href >}}'\n    title='X'\n    aria-label='X'\n    target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <iconify-icon\n      icon='fa6-brands:x-twitter'\n      width='1.5em'\n      height='1.5em'\n      aria-hidden='true'>\n    </iconify-icon>\n  </a>\n      <a\n    href='{{< var social.facebook.href >}}'\n    title='Facebook'\n    aria-label='Facebook'\n    target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <iconify-icon\n      icon='fa6-brands:facebook'\n      width='1.5em'\n      height='1.5em'\n      aria-hidden='true'>\n    </iconify-icon>\n  </a>\n      <a\n    href='{{< var social.linkedin.href >}}'\n    title='LinkedIn'\n    aria-label='LinkedIn'\n    target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <iconify-icon\n      icon='fa6-brands:linkedin'\n      width='1.5em'\n      height='1.5em'\n      aria-hidden='true'>\n    </iconify-icon>\n  </a>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n\n::: {#index-blog}\n:::\n\n<!-- \\ -->\n\n<!-- ::: {.column-screen style=\"text-align: center;\"}\n![](_resources/images/lille_cut.png)\n::: -->\n",
